videos.headline: Ole Miss gets tricky
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Chad Kelly throws a backwards pass to WR Laquon Treadwell, who throws downfield to Quincy Adeboyejo, who runs to the end zone to score a 68-yard touchdown against Memphis.
